    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Zarya bubbles herself or a diving teammate right as burst damage lands, then converts the resulting energy into a high-damage beam that melts through barriers and grouped enemies alike.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her damage output is directly tied to bubble timing; if she can't find a reason to pop a bubble, her beam and Graviton Surge both do far less work than they should.</p>"
